window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>They say that behind every great man is a great woman...but what if that woman is a werewolf? </p> <p>Settled into their new home of North Chicago, Terry and Char find more enemies than they suspected. Faced with their greatest threat, they put the FDG into action against a Forsaken who's surrounded himself with a small army of loyal humans. With Akio's aid, they go to war. </p>"; 
